    <item>
      <title>哈佛大学选择保守派律师担任重要领导角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/harvard-selects-conservative-lawyer-to-powerful-leadership-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学任命联邦法院和行政法学者约翰·曼宁为常任教务长，这是该校权力第二大的领导职位，他将负责监督学术政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/harvard-selects-conservative-lawyer-to-powerful-leadership-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
